28:02.448 --> 28:04.782
It was just sex.

28:04.784 --> 28:06.450
It didn't mean anything.

28:06.452 --> 28:10.187
And you felt terrible
afterwards.

28:10.189 --> 28:12.723
And it didn't happen
again until...

28:12.725 --> 28:14.158
(gasps softly)

28:14.160 --> 28:16.260
After you got shot.

28:30.241 --> 28:32.076
Okay.

28:33.211 --> 28:35.813
So... Twice.

28:35.815 --> 28:37.815
The first time
was after the inauguration,

28:37.817 --> 28:39.049
And then the second time...

28:39.051 --> 28:42.052
After the assassination
attempt.

28:42.054 --> 28:44.354
You had sex...

28:44.356 --> 28:46.256
Once...

28:48.893 --> 28:52.763
After you recovered
from your gunshot wounds...

28:52.765 --> 28:55.399
Because you were feeling
your mortality.

28:55.401 --> 28:57.434
Facing death.

28:59.738 --> 29:01.839
(exhales)

29:03.975 --> 29:05.342
Once on inauguration night,

29:05.344 --> 29:07.344
And once after
the assassination attempt.

29:07.346 --> 29:08.412
I'm not lying.

29:08.414 --> 29:10.047
It's still the truth.

29:10.049 --> 29:12.449
Just not the whole truth.

29:15.787 --> 29:17.354
Are we agreed?

29:24.863 --> 29:26.096
Yeah. (sighs softly)

29:36.374 --> 29:37.508
Agreed.

29:37.510 --> 29:40.544
(inhales and exhales sharply)

29:40.546 --> 29:42.146
(pounds on door)

29:43.915 --> 29:46.483
(door clanks and whirs)

29:46.485 --> 29:48.552
(door whirs and clanks closed)

29:48.554 --> 29:49.820
Liv...

29:49.822 --> 29:51.488
I'm fine.
I'm sorry.

29:51.490 --> 29:53.190
I know that wasn't easy
for you.

29:53.192 --> 29:54.158
I'm fine.

29:54.160 --> 29:56.093
I'm not.

29:58.129 --> 30:00.931
How are you?

30:00.933 --> 30:03.333
Really?
I'm... Fine.

30:03.335 --> 30:05.435
Your name's a headline.
You're not fine.

30:05.437 --> 30:07.871
I tell my clients all the time
that it's not personal.

30:07.873 --> 30:09.273
The reporters--
they're just doing their jobs.

30:09.275 --> 30:11.175
It's not personal.
It's not about me.

30:11.177 --> 30:12.309
It's the story.

30:12.311 --> 30:15.078
I'm fine.

30:20.385 --> 30:22.586
Don't.

30:23.521 --> 30:25.255
Don't. (gasps)

30:26.124 --> 30:28.892
(gasps)

30:34.365 --> 30:35.432
(exhales)

30:35.434 --> 30:38.235
(gasps)

30:40.205 --> 30:43.106
(sobbing)

30:43.108 --> 30:44.341
Mm-hmm.

30:44.343 --> 30:48.111
(continues sobbing)

30:55.086 --> 30:57.921
(sniffles)

30:57.923 --> 31:00.057
(pounds on door)

31:00.059 --> 31:02.426
(door whirs)

31:02.428 --> 31:05.162
(door whirs, clanks closed)

31:08.233 --> 31:09.967
(door opens)

31:09.969 --> 31:11.969
Thanks for seeing me
this morning, sally.

31:11.971 --> 31:13.203
(door closes)
scotch?

31:13.205 --> 31:16.206
A touch early for me, sir.

31:16.208 --> 31:18.609
How was the senate
women's caucus?

31:18.611 --> 31:21.478
Angry at you,
but I handled them.

31:21.480 --> 31:23.881
I appreciate it.
Thank you.

31:23.883 --> 31:25.616
I hope you've been
using the time wisely.

31:25.618 --> 31:27.918
I wrote a speech,

31:27.920 --> 31:30.487
Taking full responsibility.

31:30.489 --> 31:32.489
Mellie and I are facing
the press at noon today.

31:32.491 --> 31:34.992
Mellie's standing with you?

31:34.994 --> 31:36.493
So your marriage will weather
this storm.

31:36.495 --> 31:38.629
There are the children
to consider.

31:38.631 --> 31:40.998
Well, that's...

31:41.000 --> 31:43.667
I'm glad for you.

31:43.669 --> 31:46.436
It's refreshing to hear
a man valuing the family.

31:46.438 --> 31:47.671
(exhales)

31:47.673 --> 31:49.473
Good men are hard
to come by.

31:52.277 --> 31:53.677
How is dan these days?

31:53.679 --> 31:55.946
Oh, fine.

31:55.948 --> 31:57.614
Fine. (sighs)

31:57.616 --> 32:01.051
Moving to d.C. Has been
exciting for him.

32:01.053 --> 32:04.554
My husband is having just
a little bit more...

32:04.556 --> 32:07.991
Fun... These days.

32:07.993 --> 32:11.662
He's still the same
daniel douglas. He's just...

32:11.664 --> 32:13.563
Fun now.

32:17.568 --> 32:22.072
I am the most powerful woman
in the free world.

32:22.074 --> 32:25.943
There are challenges
associated with that.

32:31.049 --> 32:33.617
Sally...

32:33.619 --> 32:36.053
Yes, mr. President?

32:39.490 --> 32:41.625
After my speech,

32:41.627 --> 32:44.728
There will be a window.

32:44.730 --> 32:46.463
Climb through it.

32:46.465 --> 32:50.500
Be bold. Condemn me.

32:50.502 --> 32:53.136
Make yourself
the moral center of the party.

32:54.639 --> 32:56.974
Use the moment to rise.

32:58.643 --> 33:00.978
Can you do that?

33:02.680 --> 33:04.548
Oh, I believe I can,
mr. President.

33:07.652 --> 33:11.355
Why are you helping me?

33:11.357 --> 33:13.056
Why are you extending
kindness?

33:17.128 --> 33:19.663
Because we are not married
to one another.

33:35.513 --> 33:36.780
Why did you schedule
the press conference?

33:36.782 --> 33:38.782
Because our president
told me to.

33:38.784 --> 33:40.150
Because you had
a secret meeting.

33:40.152 --> 33:41.718
They want to go public.

33:41.720 --> 33:43.353
Again, aren't you
part of "they" now?

33:43.355 --> 33:45.589
One-third of some secret
unholy political trinity.

33:45.591 --> 33:47.457
They want to go public,
and we need to stop them

33:47.459 --> 33:48.759
And fix this.

33:48.761 --> 33:50.527
How?
Presser's in three hours.

33:50.529 --> 33:52.129
I think I have a plan.

33:52.131 --> 33:54.364
It just needs to come
from the outside.

33:54.366 --> 33:56.767
(projector and camera shutter
clicking)

33:56.769 --> 33:59.336
I feel horrible about this.
We're doing the right thing.

33:59.338 --> 34:00.704
Olivia says
what the right thing is.

34:00.706 --> 34:02.005
Look, it's not too late
to pull back.

34:02.007 --> 34:03.340
Couldn't we just
kill another intern?

34:03.342 --> 34:04.541
It wouldn't be that hard.

34:06.210 --> 34:08.245
A bad one. The worst one.

34:08.247 --> 34:09.613
All right, we need to be
united on this.

34:09.615 --> 34:10.680
Are we united on this?

34:10.682 --> 34:12.616
If I do this,
we all do this.

34:12.618 --> 34:15.085
You have to have my back.

34:18.489 --> 34:22.759
Are we gladiators,
or... Are we bitches?

34:22.761 --> 34:26.129
I need to hear it.

34:26.131 --> 34:28.465
(all) gladiators.

34:28.467 --> 34:29.866
Damn right.

34:33.671 --> 34:38.408
(projector and camera shutter
clicking)

34:40.579 --> 34:45.348
Just a couple of details about
the president's statement today.

34:45.350 --> 34:46.817
Is he gonna admit
to anything this time?

34:46.819 --> 34:48.485
'cause if it's
just another duck--

34:48.487 --> 34:52.122
Of the president's statement.
That's not why I'm here.

34:52.124 --> 34:54.658
I am here to remind you that
we're going live today...

34:54.660 --> 34:57.160
(murmuring)
at 12:04 from the... (chuckles)

34:57.162 --> 34:58.829
(man) turn that up.
Okay, come on, you guys.

34:58.831 --> 35:02.766
<i>I think that governor grant</i>
<i>has the election in the bag.</i>

35:02.768 --> 35:06.470
<i>I mean, he really cares</i>
<i>about the middle class.</i>

35:06.472 --> 35:09.272
<i>His record on social issues</i>

35:09.274 --> 35:11.508
<i>Really resonates</i>
<i>with young people.</i>

35:11.510 --> 35:13.477
<i>And... (giggles)</i>

35:13.479 --> 35:14.811
<i>Most importantly,</i>

35:14.813 --> 35:19.116
<i>He is freakin'</i> hot!

35:19.118 --> 35:20.684
(reporters shouting questions)

35:20.686 --> 35:23.153
(rick james' "super freak"
playing)

35:23.155 --> 35:24.554
<i>(james) I'm reporting to you</i>
<i>live from the white house,</i>

35:24.556 --> 35:26.356
<i>Where counter to earlier</i>
<i>erroneous reports</i>

35:26.358 --> 35:28.125
<i>Of olivia pope being...</i>

35:28.127 --> 35:30.360
<i>We now have two high-level</i>
<i>white house officials</i>

35:30.362 --> 35:33.763
<i>That 26-year-old</i>
<i>communications aide</i>

35:33.765 --> 35:36.800
<i>Jeannine locke is the other</i>
<i>woman in the grant affair.</i>

35:36.802 --> 35:39.369
You have to believe me.
People have to believe me.

35:39.371 --> 35:41.805
I never--none of this--
any of it--is true.

35:41.807 --> 35:43.807
I mean, yeah,
I called him hot.

35:43.809 --> 35:45.675
<i>(woman) sources say there are</i>
<i>multiple e-mails</i>

35:45.677 --> 35:47.410
<i>From jeannine to friends</i>

35:47.412 --> 35:49.613
<i>Detailing her strong feelings</i>
<i>for the president.</i>

35:49.615 --> 35:52.582
My name, my picture
are all over the tv.

35:52.584 --> 35:54.584
My private e-mails.

35:54.586 --> 35:56.419
Do I need a lawyer, cy?

35:56.421 --> 35:59.689
<i>"super awesome," "super cool,"</i>
<i>and "super doable"--</i>

35:59.691 --> 36:01.658
<i>Just a few of the adjectives</i>
<i>locke used in e-mails</i>

36:01.660 --> 36:03.527
<i>To describe the president.</i>

36:03.529 --> 36:04.828
Guilty people call lawyers.

36:04.830 --> 36:06.830
The white house
will handle this.

36:06.832 --> 36:09.332
I personally
will handle this.

36:09.334 --> 36:10.867
<i>(james) ...With multiple</i>
<i>sources also confirming</i>

36:10.869 --> 36:12.636
<i>Jeannine locke</i>
<i>and the president</i>

36:12.638 --> 36:15.672
<i>Had what they describe as,</i>
<i>quote, "a brief fling"...</i>

36:15.674 --> 36:18.542
You're not alone in this.
We're all here for you.

36:18.544 --> 36:20.377
You're part of the family.

36:20.379 --> 36:22.712
<i>(james) ...Those sources</i>
<i>at the same time denying</i>

36:22.714 --> 36:24.548
<i>That olivia pope had</i>
<i>any form</i>

36:24.550 --> 36:26.316
<i>Of inappropriate relationship</i>
<i>with the president.</i>

36:26.318 --> 36:30.187
<i>One thing is clear--</i>
<i>olivia pope is owed an apology.</i>

36:30.189 --> 36:32.355
Leading every net.
Of course it is.

36:32.357 --> 36:35.458
¶ that girl's all right
with me ¶

36:35.460 --> 36:38.228
<i>What</i> did you do?

36:38.230 --> 36:39.796
¶ yeah

36:39.798 --> 36:41.798
¶ hey, hey, hey, hey

36:44.336 --> 36:50.507
Calm down, honey.
What the hell is going on?
What the hell did cyrus do?

36:50.509 --> 36:51.975
What the hell did he do
to that poor, innocent girl?

36:51.977 --> 36:53.410
Jeannine?
She's a kid!

36:53.412 --> 36:54.811
What did he do?
It doesn't make any sense.

36:54.813 --> 36:56.513
We have a press conference
scheduled.

36:56.515 --> 36:58.815
You and I need to get out to
the rose garden in 20 minutes.

36:58.817 --> 37:00.784
And then we have to amend
our statements?

37:00.786 --> 37:02.586
We should call
the speechwriters,

37:02.588 --> 37:03.954
See if we can get them
to change these remarks

37:03.956 --> 37:05.522
So it's clear
that it wasn't jeannine.

37:05.524 --> 37:08.458
I don't think so.
What?

37:08.460 --> 37:10.360
You could go out there
and say that it wasn't jeannine,

37:10.362 --> 37:11.628
That it was olivia.

37:11.630 --> 37:13.997
You could say someone
must have made a mistake,

37:13.999 --> 37:15.365
Gotten the story wrong.

37:15.367 --> 37:17.434
You could.
I won't be with you.

37:17.436 --> 37:19.803
Cyrus won't stand by you.
The democrats would love that.

37:19.805 --> 37:21.871
They'd open up
a special investigation,

37:21.873 --> 37:24.341
Dig through every e-mail,
every promotion,

37:24.343 --> 37:25.942
Every late-night call log
from the oval,

37:25.944 --> 37:27.544
And then you'd get impeached.

37:27.546 --> 37:30.347
Why are you so happy
to jump on cyrus' plan

37:30.349 --> 37:33.883
"cyrus' plan." no.
See, leaking jeannine's name

37:33.885 --> 37:35.518
Was my plan.

37:35.520 --> 37:37.654
It was this <i>crazy</i> idea
I got from you.

37:37.656 --> 37:39.422
From me?
Mm.

37:39.424 --> 37:42.259
What?
After you leaked
olivia's name.

37:47.398 --> 37:49.633
(exhales)

37:51.269 --> 37:53.403
The upsetting thing about
being as educated as I am

37:53.405 --> 37:56.573
And as intelligent as I am
is that being first lady

37:56.575 --> 37:59.442
Is profoundly boring.

37:59.444 --> 38:02.412
What did you call me?
Ornamental? Not functional?

38:02.414 --> 38:04.447
I am a rose
dying on the vine here.

38:04.449 --> 38:06.783
Give me a war to run
or the c.I.A.

38:06.785 --> 38:09.452
Or something, but...

38:09.454 --> 38:13.857
I use the copious amounts
of free time I have to <i>think.</i>

38:13.859 --> 38:15.525
And I have been thinking--

38:15.527 --> 38:18.295
Who could have possibly
leaked that name, and why?

38:18.297 --> 38:19.596
And then I realized--

38:19.598 --> 38:22.432
Who would benefit the most?

38:22.434 --> 38:24.501
My idealistic,

38:24.503 --> 38:27.370
Romantic, optimistic,

38:27.372 --> 38:29.839
Idiotic husband.

38:32.076 --> 38:33.410
Sir?

38:33.412 --> 38:36.479
Shut the door, tom.
I need a favor.

38:36.481 --> 38:39.516
You want another drink?
You're buying.

38:39.518 --> 38:41.718
(indistinct conversations)

38:45.856 --> 38:47.791
Good thing he's off
tomorrow, huh?

38:47.793 --> 38:49.392
No way, tommy.

38:49.394 --> 38:51.027
Who's this trusted advisor?

38:51.029 --> 38:52.896
Mm... (chuckles)

38:52.898 --> 38:54.497
(inhales)

38:56.067 --> 38:58.802
Just between me and you,
right?

38:59.804 --> 39:01.538
It's olivia pope.

39:03.040 --> 39:04.774
You thought if you leaked
olivia's name

39:04.776 --> 39:06.776
And then I stood next to you
and held your hand

39:06.778 --> 39:08.578
And smiled while you told
the press everything you did,

39:08.580 --> 39:10.380
That it would neutralize
the situation.

39:10.382 --> 39:14.584
Stop looking for a way out
and look for a way through?

39:14.586 --> 39:16.586
Get me to play the good wife,
control me,

39:16.588 --> 39:18.455
And by extension, the nation,

39:18.457 --> 39:20.090
Because--and here's
the best part--

39:20.092 --> 39:21.491
You still somehow believe

39:21.493 --> 39:23.059
The country will eventually
embrace you

39:23.061 --> 39:26.096
Bringing your whore into
the white house as first lady.

39:26.098 --> 39:29.833
And step one--
leaking live's name. (scoffs)

39:30.835 --> 39:33.002
No.

39:33.004 --> 39:35.472
Step one...

39:35.474 --> 39:38.508
Was me to coming blair house
and laying my head in your lap

39:38.510 --> 39:40.944
<i>Like a gave a damn about</i>
<i>your forgiveness.</i>

39:40.946 --> 39:43.847
This is a war, mellie.
You and I are at war.

39:43.849 --> 39:46.449
What happened today is just
one battle of many.

39:46.451 --> 39:47.584
And let's be clear.

39:47.586 --> 39:49.886
The reason I leaked liv's name

39:49.888 --> 39:51.588
Is because as long as you had
her name

39:51.590 --> 39:55.091
In your arsenal of weapons,
olivia was at your mercy.

39:55.093 --> 39:56.626
Now she is free.

40:11.509 --> 40:13.009
Right now

40:13.011 --> 40:14.577
You're good.

40:14.579 --> 40:17.080
You're golden.

40:17.082 --> 40:19.716
You're in the clear, liv.

40:22.153 --> 40:23.820
There is nothing wrong

40:23.822 --> 40:26.523
With a little
self-preservation.

40:27.691 --> 40:29.959
Doesn't mean
you don't wear the white hat.

40:31.829 --> 40:34.864
We've got a client.
Let's get to work.

40:39.737 --> 40:41.971
It's cyrus again, jeannine.
Just trying to catch you.

40:41.973 --> 40:44.707
I know you must be scared,
but just hold tight.

40:44.709 --> 40:46.776
We'll get this
whole thing straightened.

40:46.778 --> 40:49.646
(gun cocks, switch clicks)

40:51.582 --> 40:54.851
Ooh. Sorry. Shoes on the covers.
How rude of me.

40:54.853 --> 40:56.820
Did you... Is he...

40:56.822 --> 40:59.222
Dead? (chuckles) no.

40:59.224 --> 41:01.191
He's just taking a little
drug-induced nappy.

41:01.193 --> 41:03.726
Baby's out, too.
Didn't have to drug her.

41:03.728 --> 41:05.728
That fancy swing you got
in there's worth every penny.

41:05.730 --> 41:07.163
What do you want, charlie?

41:07.165 --> 41:09.566
It's not what I want.
You know how I work.

41:09.568 --> 41:13.203
Always serving
a higher purpose.

41:13.205 --> 41:14.571
(door creaks)

41:14.573 --> 41:18.208
(water dripping faintly)

41:18.210 --> 41:19.876
I would have called,
but I couldn't risk

41:19.878 --> 41:21.878
Secret service being
anywhere near

41:21.880 --> 41:24.814
The conversation
we're about to have.

41:24.816 --> 41:27.083
Trunk was very comfortable,
thank you.

41:27.085 --> 41:29.586
Thumbprint, please.
(taps)

41:29.588 --> 41:30.854
I need to break the seal
on this, and I can't

41:30.856 --> 41:33.156
Until I raise
your security clearance.

41:33.158 --> 41:36.259
(beeps, whirs)
other hand.

41:36.261 --> 41:38.728
(whirs)
and your signature.

41:39.730 --> 41:41.064
So...

41:41.066 --> 41:42.232
(whirs)
charlie...

41:42.234 --> 41:47.237
When the republic is in danger,
there's no place for spite.

41:47.239 --> 41:49.539
If you're talking about
the president's affair

41:49.541 --> 41:51.074
With olivia--
this is bigger than that.

41:51.076 --> 41:54.244
What do you know...
About operation remington?

41:54.246 --> 41:56.713
Only that it was a classified
mission that fitz flew

41:56.715 --> 41:59.849
With jake ballard in iran
back when they were in the navy.

41:59.851 --> 42:01.184
Most of it's redacted.

42:01.186 --> 42:02.585
This...
(folder lands on table)

42:02.587 --> 42:05.188
Is what really happened
on that mission.

42:07.791 --> 42:09.559
(seal tears)

42:19.603 --> 42:21.638
Oh, my god.

42:22.606 --> 42:23.973
(gasps)

42:23.975 --> 42:25.642
(projector and camera shutter
clicks)
